This is for setting up the pro version of Burpsuite:

Step 1:run the following command

sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y wget && wget -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xiv3r/Burpsuite-Professional/main/install.sh | sudo bash

Step 2:
The License activator will have opened up, (If not, run it directly via Java -jar loader.jar present in the cloned github repo).
Click the run button at the right side. a new launcher window will be opened and you will be opted to activate the license, choose manual activation.

Step 3:
Copy the license value from loader.jar, and paste it in the launcher window asking for a license.
The launcher window will have generated an activation request, copy it into the window where you got the license (loader.jar).

Step 4:
An activation Response will have been generated, copy that and paste it into the launcher. After submitting burpsuitepro version will have been activated and you will be able to access it.



An issue you may face is due to java openjdk22 not being present, to fix that follow the following steps.
Step 1:
go to https://jdk.java.net/archive/

Step 2:
Download the java version 22 openjdk.

Step 3:
extract jdk-22

Step 4:
Move/Copy jdk-22 to /usr/lib/jvm/ you will have some version of java already present there . (you might need root permissions to move/copy the jdk-22 folder there.)

Step 5:
Switch to root and execute the following commands.
update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/java  java  /usr/lib/jvm/jdk-22/bin/java  2200
update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/javac javac /usr/lib/jvm/jdk-22/bin/javac 2200
update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/jar   jar   /usr/lib/jvm/jdk-22/bin/jar   2200

Step 6:
Run the following command and verify that java version 22 is the one chosen, if not select it and choose java version22 as the option.
sudo update-alternatives --config java

Step 7:
Rerun the steps for installing Burpsuitepro and it should now install without any issues.



For Refrence, you can check out this github repository: https://github.com/xiv3r/Burpsuite-Professional
